Date: Wed, 7 Jan 2026 16:13:12 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 02/16] fix: prevent GILE training objective from diverging to
 negative infinity

Fixes unbounded adversarial loss causing divergence during GILE training.
---
 main.py       |  38 ++++---
 model_GLIE.py | 281 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
 utils.py      |  11 ++
 3 files changed, 294 insertions(+), 36 deletions(-)

